Data binding:
JS class-> template.


Event binding:
template--> JS Class

from view to class for an operation.
ie' from an input field.

we use tempalte reference variables.


in the element in whic you want reference to:
//want reference to the input givein in an input element
<input #myInput type="text">
<button (click)="logMessage(myInput.value)">button</button>

now pass that value (myInput) to the method "logMessage"
